attribute-definition.description:
Example patterns: dr-list-{COUNTRY}-{CURRENCY}, {COUNTRY}-m-list-{CURRENCY}

Please add a text and add {COUNTRY} and {CURRENCY} placeholders in the text. 
Later these placeholders will be replaced in the code with the given country code and currency code.

Example patterns: dr-sale-{COUNTRY}-{CURRENCY}, {COUNTRY}-m-sale-{CURRENCY}

Please add a text and add {COUNTRY} and {CURRENCY} placeholders in the text. 
Later these placeholders will be replaced in the code with the given country code and currency code.
